This paper involves using social media data to analyze health behavior towards HPV vaccination, which falls under the category of social informatics (cs.SI). The paper also involves preprocessing and analyzing large amounts of data, which could fall under the categories of software development (cs.SD) and cybernetics (cs.CY). Additionally, the paper uses topic modeling and natural language processing techniques, which could fall under the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL) and social and information networks (cs.SOC).
